    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1285939453038301184",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=923540006109319168#heading-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则</a>》，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年10月15日- 2025年10月21日，规则预计于 2025年10月22日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">核心调整点：</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）售后服务流程违规-售后处理不规范中，增加&ldquo;售后服务承诺与平台服务产品不一致&rdquo;的违规场景，</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">售后服务承诺与平台服务产品不一致指：<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">商家自行承诺的特色服务、商品退换等售后服务与商家开通的平台服务产品不一致或存在过度售后承诺。</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）售后处理不规范处理措施增加：预警整改，下架违规商品的处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #e03e2d;\">&ldquo;售后服务承诺与平台服务产品不一致&rdquo; 规则解读可查阅</span>：</span></strong><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #3768fa; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1295653344178184192\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">售后承诺与平台服务产品不一致规则解读</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心修订规则内容如下：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">16</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【售后服务流程违规】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">16.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【违规定义】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增：3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、售后处理不规范：指商家在售后服务过程中存在未有效履行承诺、服务单处理多次出现问题、不合理增加消费者售后成本、违背协议或规则向消费者提供服务等妨害消费者权益的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家售后处理不规范包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）售后承诺与平台服务产品不一致：指商家自行承诺的特色服务、商品退换等售后服务与商家开通的平台服务产品不一致或存在过度售后承诺。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">②</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">16.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【处理措施】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、售后处理不规范：若经京东巡检识别或消费者反馈，店铺存在上述售后处理不规范等行为，京东有权视商家违规程度采取包括但不限于要求商家依承诺提供服务、依据对应特色服务产品规则进行处理、京东介入处理、对商家<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">进行预警整改、下架违规商品</span>、向消费者赔付、扣除100-2000元/单的违约金、为消费者执行退货退款等措施，退货运费及相应损失由商家承担。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>",
